{
  "stem": "15396.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, until one day I was sitting in a restaurant in New York, and a lady came to the door and said, oh, Charles, the detectives are looking all over Europe for you.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It turned out that my daughter was trying to find me with a detective.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then some friends of mine who live in Acapulco arranged for her to come down there and meet me there, this very close friend of mine, Ricky di Portanova and his wife.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his wife was wonderful for my daughter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave parties to make it look as if I was acceptable, to make me look good in the eyes of my daughter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very nervous, you know, to see your daughter after all those years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, 30 some years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And April is so helpful with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "April, they love her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We've been down there, and the Argentine Air Force invited me to Antarctica.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so April came and stayed with my daughter a little bit, and they get along like a house afire.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, seven children.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the six boys all play polo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes you wonder how fascinating they are.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I suppose when-- as I say, in school, we were taught you're supposed to, you know, but I got involved in the Congo thing a little bit, and Hungary.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked a good bit up there with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what I was doing, I was working with-- most of them were Knights of Malta.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, I became a Knight when they put me in the Knights of Malta, too, but not with that group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were bringing people from the frontier to, you know, tell them where to go and so forth.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We spent the whole winter up there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
